flowchart TD
    A([Inscription]) --> B{Rôle ?}
    B -->|Joueur| C[Accès standard]
    B -->|Coach / Agent| D[Upload document obligatoire]
    D --> E[(is_verified = false\nstatus = PENDING)]
    E --> F[Badge orange]
    F --> G{Admin}
    G -->|OK| H[(VERIFIED)]
    G -->|KO| I[(REJECTED)]
    H --> J[Badge vert + messagerie]
    I --> K[Ré-upload]
